properties.script:
import datetime

mydate=datetime.date.today()
year, month= divmod(mydate.month-1, 12)
if month == 0: 
      month = 12
      year = year -1
one_month = datetime.datetime(mydate.year + year, month, mydate.day)
millisec = int(one_month.timestamp() * 1000)

year3, month3= divmod(mydate.month-3, 12)
if month3 == 0: 
      month3 = 12
      year3 = year3 -1
three_months = datetime.datetime(mydate.year + year3, month3, mydate.day)
three_millisec = int(three_months.timestamp() * 1000)
